This involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques, which are commonly used in the computer science subfields of digital libraries (cs.DL), computational linguistics (cs.CL), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
